| ------------- | --------------------------- | ----- | ------------------------------- |
| `BaseGrid`    | Main grid orchestrator      | ~432  | Complete grid with all features |
| `GridToolbar` | Action buttons and controls | ~108  | CRUD operations, undo/redo      |
